    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494340/extras/D_Corp_Divider_About_600.png?t=1667920658\" /></span><br><br><strong>D-Corp</strong> is a crazy couch co-op game for up to 4 players. Play as a team of cute, customizable robots. Fulfill the corporate dreams of your brainy boss. Work together on tasks such as turret maintenance and harvesting natural resources while being under continuous attack by alien cacti!<br><br>Enjoy the dynamic gameplay in this light-hearted game about silly attempts at teamwork!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494340/extras/D_Corp_Divider_Customization_600.png?t=1667920658\" /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494340/extras/cosmetics.gif?t=1667920658\" /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494340/extras/D_Corp_Divider_Features_600.png?t=1667920658\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>2-, 3-, or 4-player co-op through local play or via Steam Remote Play 👫🎮🎮<br></li><li>Avoid dangerous cacti and stop them from overrunning your base<br></li><li>Experiment with different defense plans!<br></li><li>Scrap all resources and carry them back to your recycler 🔨🤖<br></li><li>Throw your friend into deadly acid pool! <br></li><li>Reload, maintain and relocate a variety of turrets to protect your operation <br></li><li>Find, unlock, and wear dozens of shiny hats! 🧢🎩🤠<br></li><li>Fetch ammo in time before the turrets run out -- throw it if you have to!<br></li><li>This game was designed to be played with <strong>gamepads.</strong></li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494340/extras/D_Corp_Divider_Gameplay_600.png?t=1667920658\" /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494340/extras/gameplay.gif?t=1667920658\" /></span>",
